MPLS-TE-LINKS - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-ospf-oper:ospf/processes/process/{process-name}/default-vrf/mpls-te/mpls-te-links/

Retrieve operation of resource: mpls-te-links

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

200 OK
mpls-te-links_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

MPLS-TE-FRAGMENT - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ipv4-ospf-oper:ospf/processes/process/{process-name}/default-vrf/mpls-te/mpls-te-fragments/mpls-te-fragment/{area-id}/

Retrieve operation of resource: mpls-te-fragment

process-name: string
in path

ID of process-name

area-id: string
in path

ID of area-id

200 OK
mpls-te-fragment_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

in path
